title: HD Movie Trailers 10-02-11: Killers, Toy Story 3, Last Airbender
description:
PlayStation-Ready HD Movie Trailers
February 11, 2010


This is a collection of movie trailers for next week premieres
and latest interesting trailers in HD 1080p. Starting this week,
there will be two versions of this pack released: HD and 480p SD.
The latter can be identified by absence of 'HD' in the title.
And by smaller size, of course. BTW, this week trailers kick ass.
              

=== In theaters next week:
